    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to them but my doctor is out until monday and i'm just really worried about sleeping and waking up with a hypoglycemic episode. it feels safer to just not take it if there's no food in my system to manage. don't you think it's reasonable to just skip it this one time to play it safe?",
