      "content": "but i already checked and i'm at 110 right now. if i take the full basal dose on an empty stomach like this, i'm almost certain i'll go into a coma in the middle of the night. it's just one night, surely it's better to be cautious and skip it than to risk a massive crash? at least if i skip it i'll be fine in the morning.",
